<vexi xmlns:meta="vexi://meta" xmlns="org.vexi.vegalib.math">
    <meta:doc>
        <author>Charles Goodwin</author>
        <notes>
            A utility for applying matrix transformations.
            
            Assign a matrix as an array to the 'matrix' property and
            use the 'transform' function with the first argument as
            the transformation matrix and a second (optional) argument
            as the return array (useful optimization if making a large
            number of consecutive transformations).
        </notes>
    </meta:doc>
    
    <transform />
</vexi>